{ hello_ga68.a68 -- minimal GNU Algol 68 (ga68) program.            }
{ ga68 uses the MODERN stropping regime: lowercase bold words and   }
{ { } comments, unlike a68g's UPPER BEGIN/END and # ... # comments. }
{ Build: ga68 -g hello_ga68.a68 -o hello_ga68   (native, gdb-able)  }
begin
   puts ("Hello, GNU Algol 68!'n")
end
